Class Simulator.Params

  • java.lang.Object
    • Simulator.Params
  • Enclosing class:
    Simulator

    private class Simulator.Params
extends java.lang.Object
    Params is a private container class for all configuration parameters of this simulation.

      • Params

        public Params​(java.lang.String[] args)
        Initialize the parameters either from the standard input or from a given input file (specified by filename).
        Parameters:
        args - the command line argument. If none is given, read from standard input. Else, assume args[0] is the input filename, and read from that file.
